lead_paragraph: Kirsten Honeycutt hit a run-scoring single in the top of the sixth inning to lead the South team from Morristown, Tenn., to a 3-2 victory over the Southwest team from Elgin, Tex., in the championship game of the Little League Softball World Series in Portland, Ore.
